								<p class="h_services">This office heads the following services:</p>
								
								<div id="h_BILLDRAFTING">
								<p><a href="javascript:ShowHide('BILLDRAFTING')">Legislative Bill Drafting Service</a></p>
								</div>
								<div id="BILLDRAFTING" class="iL2">
									<p class="OfficeDesc">Legislative Bill 
									Drafting Service renders assistance to the 
									members of the Senate in the drafting of bills 
